title: SP Warsaw - Endangering the Welfare of a Child (New York State Division of State ...
text: ( Source : New York State Division of State Police ) PRESS RELEASE Oct 13 - New York State Police in Warsaw arrested James C. Robbins , 25 years of age of Attica, NY for two counts of Endangering the Welfare of a Child ( Class A Misdemeanor ).
